  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>(This Jutsu cannot score a critical hit).</strong></em></p><p>You pause and enter a state of absolute serenity and determination, remembering the face of your father. For the duration of this jutsu, you do not spend Chakra to maintain it.</p><p>Mark up to five creatures within weapon range, reducing your ammunition dice by 1 step for each marked creature. At the start of your next turn, make a single ranged Taijutsu attack against each marked creature at advantage, regardless of range.</p><p>On a hit, they take your [Weapon Damage] + 12d12. If you mark and hit only a single creature, that creature takes double damage.</p>",
